

Deploy Android 4.4 package is not bundle exactly 
react-native start && react-native bundle --platform android --dev false --entry-file index.android.js --bundle-output android/app/src/main/assets/index.android.bundle --sourcemap-output android/app/src/main/assets/index.android.map --assets-dest android/app/src/main/res/

ListView
https://github.com/spencexyz/ListViewSample/blob/master/components/Row.js
Guide https://medium.com/differential/react-native-basics-how-to-use-the-listview-component-a0ec44cf1fe8


I got a "Unable to download JS bundle" error on the device when I tried to run it on a KitKat device
I solved it by building the bundle file using the command

curl "http://localhost:8081/index.android.bundle?platform=android" -o "android/app/src/main/assets/index.android.bundle"

followed by react-native run-android

